uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.servlet.config

Class ServletConfigService

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.servlet.config.ServletConfigService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AppContextCleanup, AppContextService<ConfigService>, ConfigService, Contexed

    public class ServletConfigService
extends java.lang.Object
implements ConfigService
    ConfigService that augments the properties with Servlet InitParams. This needs to be added to the AppContext within the servlet itself after any caching ConfigServices and once the ServletConfig is available.
